sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(kubectl)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as OGX Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as OGX Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ConfigMap as Immutable ConfigMap<br/>(content-hashed)
    participant OGXPod as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,OGXPod: Flow 1: Webhook Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS (service-serving-cert), mTLS
    Note right of Webhook: Validates:<br/>• Distribution name<br/>• Provider ID uniqueness<br/>• Model→provider refs<br/>• Adoption annotations
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit/Reject response<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/rejected

    Note over User,OGXPod: Flow 2: OGXServer Reconciliation

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer created/updated<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
    Operator->>OCI: Fetch image manifest & labels<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Anonymous
    OCI-->>Operator: com.ogx.config.* labels<br/>(base config YAML)

    Note over Operator: Config Generation Pipeline:<br/>1. Resolve base config (OCI labels / ConfigMap)<br/>2. Expand typed provider specs → config YAML<br/>3. Merge user overrides<br/>4. Produce content-hashed ConfigMap

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read user ConfigMaps/Secrets<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ConfigMap/Secret data

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create immutable ConfigMap (content-hashed)<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token

    Note over Operator: Kustomize Manifest Rendering:<br/>5-stage plugin chain:<br/>1. Name Prefix<br/>2. Namespace<br/>3. Field Mutator (RFC 6901)<br/>4. NetworkPolicy Transformer<br/>5. Autoscaling Handler

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment, Service,<br/>PVC, NetworkPolicy, HPA, PDB,<br/>Ingress, ServiceAccount, RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources reconciled

    Note over User,OGXPod: Flow 3: Status Polling

    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321, Plaintext, No auth
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Health status

    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321, Plaintext, No auth
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Provider discovery response

    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321, Plaintext, No auth
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Version info

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
